name: City of the Tombs - 006
description: An ancient city stands - on mountains, stone and steel.  Bought and paid, the graves were laid:  millenia spanning deal.  But in each generation, they rise to kill again.  Our ties bonded in blood and earth EXCLUSIVELY ON HEN.  This series was created by artificial intelligence from about 40 or so different photographs.  This is my genesis piece on hic et nunc.
